    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Swellings on a surface, often bubble-shaped, frequently caused by nonadherence or by separation of an applied substance.</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>English</Note_Language>
        <Note_Contributors>
